<div class="full"><h3>Contact Us</h3>

<p><em>If you have questions about how to use this website or Library policies, first check out the <a target="_self" href="../howto/index.php" title="">How Do I</a> and <a target="_self" href="cplpolicies/policies/index.php" title="">Policies</a> sections of the website.</em></p>
<img class="alignleft" src="../dir_images/branches/hwlc.jpg" border="0" alt="Harold Washington Library Center"/>
<p><ORG>Chicago Public Library</ORG>
<br/><STREET>400 S. State Street</STREET>
<br/><CITY>Chicago</CITY>, <STATE>IL</STATE> <ZIPCODE>60605</ZIPCODE>
<br/><TEL>(312) 747-4300</TEL></p>

<p><strong><a href="http://www.chipublib.org/library/locator/">Find your local library »</a></strong></p>
<h4>Ask a Librarian</h4>

<p>Ask a reference librarian for assistance with:</p>
<ul class="bullets"><li>Research</li>
<li>Locating library materials</li>
</ul><ul class="bullets"><li>Book, movie and music recommendations</li>
<li>Using library resources and services</li>
</ul>
<p><img class="alignleft" src="../dir_images/icons/email_60x60.jpg" border="0" alt="email icon"/><strong>By Email</strong>
<br/><a target="_self" href="asklibform.php" title="">Submit a reference question</a> and receive a reply within two business days from a professional librarian.</p>

<p><img class="alignleft" src="../dir_images/icons/phone60x60.jpg" border="0" alt="phone icon"/><strong>By Phone</strong>
<br/>The Information Center offers quick reference assistance over the phone. Call <TEL>(312) 747-4300</TEL> for assistance. Hours: <HOURS>Monday through Thursday, 9:00 a.m.-9:00 p.m.; Friday and Saturday, 9:00 a.m.-5:00 p.m.; Sunday 1:00 p.m.-5:00 p.m.</HOURS></p>
<div class="border clearfix">
</div><br/><h4>eBooks and eAudiobooks Support</h4>

<p>Didn’t find answers to your questions in <a href="http://overdrive.chipublib.org/help.htm">OverDrive Help</a> ? <a target="_self" href="../cplbooksmovies/overdrive.php" title="">Contact support</a> for assistance.</p>
<div class="border clearfix">
</div><br/><h4>My CPL Account Assistance</h4>

<p>Online instructions are available to help you <a target="_self" href="../howto/whatismycpl.php" title="access My CPL account">access your My CPL account</a> , <a target="_self" href="../howto/whatstatus.php" title="find library card status">check the status of your account</a> , track library materials on hold and <a target="_self" href="../howto/renewlib.php" title="about renewing library materials">renew items</a> currently checked out. Updating personal information and resolving account problems must be done in person at any <a href="http://www.chipublib.org/library/locator/">Chicago Public Library location</a> .</p>
<div class="border clearfix">
</div><br/><h4>Suggest a Purchase</h4>

<p><a target="_self" href="../cplbooksmovies/suggestion.php" title="">Suggest a purchase</a> to be considered by the Chicago Public Library.</p>
<div class="border clearfix">
</div><br/><h4><SUBJ>Website Comments</SUBJ></h4>

<p>Email comments or questions about the website to <a href="mailto:webmaster@chipublib.org"><EMAIL>webmaster@chipublib.org</EMAIL></a> . This account is monitored during <HOURS>business hours Monday through Friday</HOURS>. You will receive a response within two business days. We welcome your feedback.</p>
<div class="border clearfix">
</div><br/><h4><SUBJ>General Questions</SUBJ></h4>
<ul class="bullets"><li>Email <a href="mailto:info@chipublib.org"><EMAIL>info@chipublib.org</EMAIL></a> with all other questions or comments. This account is monitored during <HOURS>business hours Monday through Friday</HOURS>. You will receive a response within two business days.</li>
<li>Contact <a target="_self" href="senior_staff.php" title="">administrative staff</a> .</li>
</ul><div class="border clearfix">
</div><br/><h4>FOIA Request</h4>

<p>The Freedom of Information Act (FOIA) is a state law that provides citizens with access to public records. Visit <a target="_self" href="foia.php" title="">CPL’s FOIA page</a> to request information about the Chicago Public Library or the services offered.</p>
